\pard\nowidctlpar\qc\lang1033 DUMBLEDORE \emdash  THE TRUTH AT LAST?\lang3081\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\fi284\qj\lang1033 Coming next week, the shocking story of the flawed genius considered by many to be the greatest wizard of his generation. Stripping away the popular image of serene, silver-bearded wisdom, Rita Skeeter reveals the disturbed childhood, the lawless youth, the life\-long feuds, and the guilty secrets that Dumbledore carried to his grave. WHY was the man tipped to be Minister of Magic content to remain a mere head\-master? WHAT was the real purpose of the secret organization known as the Order of the Phoenix? HOW did Dumbledore really meet his end?\lang3081\par
