\lang1033\ldblquote Oh,\rdblquote  said Harry. \ldblquote Well, yeah. We are.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 The mangle turned of its own accord in a corner, wringing out what looked like one of Mr. Weasley\rquote s vests.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote May I ask \i why\i0  you are abandoning your education?\rdblquote  said Mrs. Weasley.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Well, Dumbledore left me \'85 stuff to do,\rdblquote  mumbled Harry. \ldblquote Ron and Hermione know about it, and they want to come too.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
