\lang1033\ldblquote Dumbledore didn\rquote t want anyone else to know, Mrs. Weasley. I\rquote m sorry. Ron and Hermione don\rquote t have to come, it\rquote s their choice \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I don\rquote t see that\lang3081  \lang1033\i you\i0  have to go either!\rdblquote  she snapped, dropping all pretense now. \ldblquote You\rquote re barely of age, any of you! It\rquote s utter nonsense, if Dumbledore needed work doing, he had the whole Order at his command! Harry, you must have misunderstood him. Probably he was telling you something he \i wanted\i0  done, and you took it to mean that he wanted \i you\i0  \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
