\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote m doing it, I\rquote m doing \emdash  ! Oh, it\rquote s you,\rdblquote  said Ron in relief, as Harry entered the room. Ron lay back down on the bed, which he had evidently just vacated. The room was just as messy as it had been all week; the only change was that Hermione was now sitting in the far corner, her fluffy ginger cat, Crookshanks, at her feet, sorting books, some of which Harry recognized as his own, into two enormous piles.\lang3081\par
