\lang1033\ldblquote Well, all right, if you want him to be dead,\rdblquote  said Ron grumpily, punching his pillow into a more comfortable shape.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Of course we don\rquote t want him to be dead!\rdblquote  said Hermione, looking shocked. \ldblquote It\rquote s dreadful that he\rquote s dead! But we\rquote re being realistic!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
