\lang1033\ldblquote  \lquote C-constant vigilance,\rquote  \rdblquote  said Hermione, mopping her eyes.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote That\rquote s right,\rdblquote  said Ron, nodding. \ldblquote He\rquote d tell us to learn from what happened to him. And what I\rquote ve learned is not to trust that cowardly little squit, Mundungus.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Hermione gave a shaky laugh and leaned forward to pick up two more books. A second later, Ron had snatched his arm back from around her shoulders; she had dropped \i The Monster Book of Monsters\i0  on his foot. The book had broken free from its restraining belt and snapped viciously at Ron\rquote s ankle.\lang3081\par
