\lang1033\ldblquote Let\rquote s see,\rdblquote  said Hermione, slamming \i Travels with Trolls\i0  onto the discarded pile with a rather fierce look. \ldblquote I\rquote ve been packing for days, so we\rquote re ready to leave at a moment\rquote s notice, which for your information has included doing some pretty difficult magic, not to mention smuggling Mad-Eye\rquote s whole stock of Polyjuice Potion right under Ron\rquote s mum\rquote s nose.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote ve also modified my parents\rquote  memories so that they\rquote re con\-vinced they\rquote re really called Wendell and Monica Wilkins, and that their life\rquote s ambition is to move to Australia, which they have now done. That\rquote s to make it more difficult for Voldemort to track them\lang3081  \lang1033 down and interrogate them about me \emdash  or you, because unfortu\-nately, I\rquote ve told them quite a bit about you.\lang3081\par
