\lang1033\ldblquote Once we\rquote ve left, the ghoul\rquote s going to come and live down here in my room,\rdblquote  said Ron. \ldblquote I think he\rquote s really looking forward to it \emdash  well, it\rquote s hard to tell, because all he can do is moan and drool \emdash  but he nods a lot when you mention it. Anyway, he\rquote s going to be me with spattergroit. Good, eh?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
