\lang1033\ldblquote I was selling in Diagon Alley and she come up to me and asks if I\rquote ve got a license for trading in magical artifacts. Bleedin\rquote  snoop. She was gonna fine me, but she took a fancy to the locket an\rquote  told me she\rquote d take it and let me off that time, and to fink meself lucky.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
