\ldblquote Harry, stop.\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote What\rquote s wrong?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 They had only just reached the grave of the unknown Abbott.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote There\rquote s someone there. Someone watching us. I can tell. There, over by the bushes.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 They stood quite still, holding on to each other, gazing at the dense black boundary of the graveyard. Harry could not see anything.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Are you sure?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I saw something move, I could have sworn I did. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 She broke from him to free her wand arm.\lang3081\par
