\lang1033 He drummed lightly on the top of the radio with his wand, mut\-tering random words under his breath. He threw Hermione many covert glances, plainly fearing an angry outburst, but for all the no\-tice she took of him he might not have been there. For ten minutes or so Ron tapped and muttered, Hermione turned the pages of her book, and Harry continued to practice with the blackthorn wand.\lang3081\par
