\lang1033 Hermione did not deign to respond, but approached Harry.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote We need to talk,\rdblquote  she said.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 He looked at the book still clutched in her hand. It was \i The Life and Lies of\lang3081  \lang1033 Albus Dumbledore.\lang3081\i0\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What?\rdblquote  he said apprehensively. It flew through his mind that there was a chapter on him in there; he was not sure he felt up to hearing Rita\rquote s version of his relationship with Dumbledore. Hermi\-one\rquote s answer, however, was completely unexpected.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I want to go and see Xenophilius Lovegood.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
