\lang1033\ldblquote Er \emdash  what are you \emdash  ?\rdblquote  said Ron tentatively, but Hermione quelled him with a look and turned back to Harry.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote It keeps cropping up, doesn\rquote t it?\rdblquote  she said. \ldblquote I know Viktor said it was Grindelwald\rquote s mark, but it was definitely on that old grave in Godric\rquote s Hollow, and the dates on the headstone were long before Grindelwald came along! And now this! Well, we can\rquote t ask Dumble\-dore or Grindelwald what it means \emdash  I don\rquote t even know whether Grindelwald\rquote s still alive \emdash  but we can ask Mr. Lovegood. He was wearing the symbol at the wedding. I\rquote m sure this is important, Harry!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
