\lang1033\ldblquote It won\rquote t be like Godric\rquote s Hollow,\rdblquote  Ron added, \ldblquote Lovegood\rquote s on your side, Harry, \i The Quibbler\rquote s\i0  been for you all along, it keeps tell\-ing everyone they\rquote ve got to help you!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
