\lang1033\ldblquote I know \rquote e\rquote s swollen, ma\rquote am, but it\rquote s \rquote im!\rdblquote  piped up Scabior. \ldblquote If you look a bit closer, you\rquote ll see \rquote is scar. And this \rquote ere, see the girl? The Mudblood who\rquote s been traveling around with \rquote im, ma\rquote am. There\rquote s no doubt it\rquote s \rquote im, and we\rquote ve got \rquote is wand as well! \rquote Ere, ma\rquote am \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Through his puffy eyelids Harry saw Narcissa Malfoy scrutiniz\-ing his swollen face. Scabior thrust the blackthorn wand at her. She raised her eyebrows.\lang3081\par
