\lang1033 Harry had never heard Lucius Malfoy so excited.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Draco, if we are the ones who hand Potter over to the Dark Lord, everything will be forgiv \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Now, we won\rquote t be forgetting who actually caught him, I hope, Mr. Malfoy?\rdblquote  said Greyback menacingly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Of course not, of course not!\rdblquote  said Lucius impatiently. He ap\-proached Harry himself, came so close that Harry could see the usually languid, pale face in sharp detail even through his swollen eyes. With his face a puffy mask, Harry felt as though he was peer\-ing out from between the bars of a cage.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What did you do to him?\rdblquote  Lucius asked Greyback. \ldblquote How did he get into this state?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote That wasn\rquote t us.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
