\lang1033 The drawing room door opened behind Harry. A woman spoke,\lang3081  \lang1033 and the sound of the voice wound Harry\rquote s fear to an even higher pitch.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What is this? What\rquote s happened, Cissy?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Bellatrix Lestrange walked slowly around the prisoners, and stopped on Harry\rquote s right, staring at Hermione through her heavily lidded eyes.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote But surely,\rdblquote  she said quietly, \ldblquote this is the Mudblood girl? This is Granger?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yes, yes, it\rquote s Granger!\rdblquote  cried Lucius. \ldblquote And beside her, we think, Potter! Potter and his friends, caught at last!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Potter?\rdblquote  shrieked Bellatrix, and she backed away, the better to take in Harry. \ldblquote Are you sure? Well then, the Dark Lord must be informed at once!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 She dragged back her left sleeve: Harry saw the Dark Mark burned into the flesh of her arm, and knew that she was about to touch it, to summon her beloved master \emdash\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I was about to call him!\rdblquote  said Lucius, and his hand actually closed upon Bellatrix\rquote s wrist, preventing her from touching the Mark. \ldblquote\i I\i0  shall summon him, Bella, Potter has been brought to my house, and it is therefore upon my authority \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Your authority!\rdblquote  she sneered, attempting to wrench her hand from his grasp. \ldblquote You lost your authority when you lost your wand, Lucius! How dare you! Take your hands off me!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
