\lang1033\ldblquote No,\rdblquote  said Ollivander. \ldblquote Whether it \i needs\i0  to pass by murder, I do not know. Its history is bloody, but that may be simply due to the fact that it is such a desirable object, and arouses such passions in wizards. Immensely powerful, dangerous in the wrong hands, and an object of incredible fascination to all of us who study the power of wands.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Mr. Ollivander,\rdblquote  said Harry, \ldblquote you told You-Know-Who that Gregorovitch had the Elder Wand, didn\rquote t you?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
