\lang1033\ldblquote It was a rumor,\rdblquote  whispered Ollivander. \ldblquote A rumor, years and years ago, long before you were born! I believe Gregorovitch himself started it. You can see how good it would be for business: that he was studying and duplicating the qualities of the Elder Wand!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yes, I can see that,\rdblquote  said Harry. He stood up. \ldblquote Mr. Ollivander, one last thing, and then we\rquote ll let you get some rest. What do you know about the Deathly Hallows?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
