\lang1033\ldblquote Thank you,\rdblquote  said Harry. \ldblquote Thank you very much. We\rquote ll leave you to get some rest now.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Ollivander looked stricken.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote He was torturing me!\rdblquote  he gasped. \ldblquote The Cruciatus Curse \'85 you have no idea. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
