\lang1033 There was a bang on the front door. Everyone\rquote s head turned to\-ward it. Fleur came running out of the kitchen, looking frightened; Bill jumped to his feet, his wand pointing at the door; Harry, Ron, and Hermione did the same. Silently Griphook slipped beneath the table, out of sight.\lang3081\par
