\lang1033 Lupin fell over the threshold. He was white-faced, wrapped in a traveling cloak, his graying hair windswept. He straightened up, looked around the room, making sure of who was there, then cried aloud, \ldblquote It\rquote s a boy! We\rquote ve named him Ted, after Dora\rquote s father!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
