\lang1033\ldblquote Yes \emdash  yes \emdash  a boy,\rdblquote  said Lupin again, who seemed dazed by his own happiness. He strode around the table and hugged Harry; the scene in the basement of Grimmauld Place might never have happened.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote You\rquote ll be godfather?\rdblquote  he said as he released Harry.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote M-me?\rdblquote  stammered Harry\lang3081\par
