\lang1033\ldblquote Well,\rdblquote  Travers coughed, \ldblquote I \i heard\i0  that the inhabitants of Malfoy Manor were confined to the house, after the \'85 ah \'85 \i escape.\i0\rdblquote\lang3081\par
