\lang1033\ldblquote Some of these wandless can be troublesome,\rdblquote  said Travers. \ldblquote While they do nothing but beg I have no objection, but one of them actually asked me to plead her case at the Ministry last week. \lquote\i I\rquote m a witch, sir, I\rquote m a witch, let me prove it to you\i0 !\rquote  \rdblquote\i  \i0 he said in a squeaky impersonation. \ldblquote As if I was going to give her my wand \emdash  but whose wand,\rdblquote  said Travers curiously, \ldblquote are you using at the moment, Bel\-latrix? I heard that your own was \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
