\lang1033\ldblquote How long\rquote s this been here?\rdblquote  Ron asked as they set off. \ldblquote It isn\rquote t on the Marauder\rquote s Map, is it, Harry? I thought there were only seven passages in and out of school?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
