\lang1033\ldblquote Ah, yes, I remember,\rdblquote  said Voldemort, looking down at Neville, who was struggling back to his feet, unarmed and unprotected, standing in the no-man\rquote s-land between the survivors and the Death Eaters. \ldblquote But you are a pureblood, aren\rquote t you, my brave boy?\rdblquote  Volde\-mort asked Neville, who stood facing him, his empty hands curled in fists.\lang3081\par
