\lang1033 Still watching through his lashes, Harry saw Voldemort wave his wand. Seconds later, out of one of the castle\rquote s shattered windows, something that looked like a misshapen bird flew through the half light and landed in Voldemort\rquote s hand. He shook the mildewed ob\-ject by its pointed end and it dangled, empty and ragged: the Sort\-ing Hat.\lang3081\par
